    %h2.appbanner__bannerContent--contentTitle
      だれでもかんたん、人生を変えるフリマアプリ
    %p.appbanner__bannerContent--contentText
      今すぐ無料ダウンロード!
    .badge-a
      = link_to "https://www.apple.com/jp/ios/app-store/", class: "aBadge" do
        = image_tag 'app_Badge.jpeg', height: 53, wigth:200, class: 'appBadge'
      = link_to "https://play.google.com/store", class: "gBadge" do
        = image_tag 'google_badge.png', height: 79, width: 180, class: 'googleBadge'

